Package graph

Interface Graph<L extends java.lang.Number,​N>

  • Type Parameters:
    L - the type of the edge length.
    N - the type of the vertex name.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdjacencyList, AdjacencyMatrix, IncidenceMatrix
    public interface Graph<L extends java.lang.Number,​N>
    The Graph interface defines the basic structure and operations for a graph data structure.
